                        NOK 10 million to opening process in the Jan Mayen area
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">National Budget 2011</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Petroleum and Energy, 05.10.2010]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian Government proposes ten million kroner for environmental studies in connection with the ongoing process to open the sea areas surrounding the island of Jan Mayen for petroleum activities.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
