                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 01.10.2010]</p>
                <p>Norway and Greece have agreed on the allocation of the EEA and Norway Grants for the period 2009–2014. The asylum area is a priority sector, and will receive NOK 152 million over the five-year period. </p>
                
                
