                        Hans Petter Graver to head new OECD National Contact Point 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Ministry of Foreign Affairs, 29.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Professor Hans Petter Graver has been appointed head of the new Norwegian National Contact Point for the OECD Guidelines for Multinational Enterprises. Foreign Minister Jonas Gahr Støre commented, “I am delighted that four such competent people have agreed to act as the contact point that will monitor Norwegian companies’ compliance with the OECD Guidelines.” </p>
                
                
